PART IV: DEFINITIVE ASYMPTOTIC ANALYSIS
========================================================================

CAREFUL ANALYSIS of H/E[H]:

Both ratios grow, but they grow at DIFFERENT RATES.
  log(H/E[H]) = log(2) + o(1)?  No, let me compute directly.

